OL,7,FPolice have ordered work to stop on
OL,8,Fpart of the 10-acre plot at Abbots
OL,9,FLeigh in North Somerset to protect
OL,10,Fnesting birds but it will still
OL,11,Fpartially open to the public this
OL,12,FSaturday (1 June).JTV wildlife expert
OL,13,FChris Packham has joined local people
OL,14,Fin criticising the location and safety
OL,15,Fof the site but the company
OL,16,Fresponsible insists it's one solution
OL,17,Fto better food production.
