OL,3,CThousands protest over plans for giant
OL,4,Callotment site on North Somerset
OL,5,Cfarmland
OL,7,FThe arguments date back more than a
OL,8,Fyear and have, at times, needed police
OL,9,Fintervention to assess claims of
OL,10,Fphysical assault.JLocals' distrust of
OL,11,Foperators Roots Allotments stems from
OL,12,Fwhat they claim is a lack of
OL,13,Fconsultation and clandestine movements
OL,14,Fof early morning vehicles dumping
OL,15,Fhundreds of tons of compost on the
OL,16,Fsite.JBut Roots co-founder Ed Morrison
OL,17,Fdisputes a lack of contact and says
OL,18,Fthe site is answering a desperate need
OL,19,Ffrom people who want to grow their own.
