OL,3,CThousands protest over plans for giant
OL,4,Callotment site on North Somerset
OL,5,Cfarmland
OL,7,F"The message we're getting from people
OL,8,Fin Bristol is they need a growing
OL,9,Fspace and unfortunately, the council
OL,10,Fand government aren't doing enough to
OL,11,Fprovide that right now," he added.
OL,12,FRoots don't need planning permission
OL,13,Fto operate the land, leased to them by
OL,14,Fdescendants of the Wills tobacco
OL,15,Ffamily. A Certificate of Lawful
OL,16,FDevelopment allows allotments as an
OL,17,Fagricultural use but prevents the
OL,18,Flaying of a hard surface for parking.
OL,19,FSophy Gretton lives yards from the
OL,20,Fentrance Roots has created close to
OL,21,Fthe A369.JShe explained: "We want them
OL,22,F(Roots) to at least understand what
OL,23,Fthey're coming to, the precious nature
OL,24,Fof this landscape and the hazards on
OL,25,Fthe main road.
