OL,5,Cfarmland
OL,7,FWhile North Somerset Council says it
OL,8,Fwill act on any alleged planning
OL,9,Fbreaches, Mr Morrison claims the
OL,10,Fbigger issue is giving people the
OL,11,Fchance to produce their own food and
OL,12,Fimprove sustainability.J"A lot of
OL,13,Fpeople said this was a fantastic idea,
OL,14,Fexactly what society needs but this is
OL,15,Fthe wrong place," he claimed. "My
OL,16,Fquestion is where is the right place
OL,17,Fwhen green spaces are getting
OL,18,Fswallowed up in cities and we have a
OL,19,Flot of agricultural land surrounding
OL,20,Fwhere we are."
